; Coverage test for textual.cc L222-224
; Tests 'h' and 'b' directives which are recognized by the parser
; as timelog-related directives and silently ignored (break).
; The 'h' line must have a space+argument to pass general_directive
; without error, then fall through to the timelog handler.

h something
b something

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
